37512312\" /><br><br><strong>Complete a variety of diverse story quests and meet unique characters inhabiting the game world</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683150/extras/Pumpkin.gif?t=1737512312\" /><br><br><strong>Engage in whatever your heart desires</strong><br>Tavern management, cooking, decorating your tavern and crafting, delivering orders, growing plants, breeding animals, hunting, fishing, and much more<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683150/extras/Tavern.gif?t=1737512312\" /><br><br><strong>Fight against a variety of enemies and monsters using different types of weapons</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683150/extras/Fight.gif?t=1737512312\" /><br><br>Dive into an ocean of fun and complete freedom of action. Play the way you want and enjoy true pleasure! The Ale &amp; Tale tavern awaits its heroes!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"So what's next?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683150/6e369605e7c524f6aa8e0475d906bca3cbd12626.jpg"},{"name":"Hail the Magic weed!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683150/a7239467b4cde820b799ce8f24dbd50db8a4adbb.jpg"},{"name":"Let the light in!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683150/0e17c29fe02182f4d9482ef323cf869186e94b40.jpg"},{"name":"No pay, no food!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683150/59b5d5c130f36c9cfe50a5861c55b38678e6d9a8.jpg"},{"name":"I should not drink at work","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2683150/6736a1221b866093a3586bb1838c0c13f75094ef.jpg"},{"name":"It's much more comfortable this way","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps